SystemRequirements: Grade-integer-program phases use Gurobi (>= 10.0)
    for the default replication backend (Gurobi license; gurobi_cl on
    PATH) or explicit open backends: the direct highs package for HiGHS and
    ROI plugins for GLPK/SYMPHONY. The package installs, loads, and tests
    without a solver license.
